  "type": "spell",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You reach out towards one creature you can see within range whose Challenge Rating is 6 or lower, gaining insight into its biology and gaining some of its powers for yourself. The DM reads you the names of its traits, of which you can select one. You gain that trait for the duration of this spell.</p><p>If the targeted creature does not have any traits, you instead gain a +1 bonus to AC for the duration.</p><p><strong><em>At Higher Levels:</em></strong> If you cast this spell using a spell slot of 3rd level or higher, you can target a creature whose Challenge Rating is not higher than three times the level of the spell slot expended.</p>",
